39.content:
----
## Dynamic bill of material (DBOM) Generated from build
---
Uncover
* unwanted packages, package versions
* unwanted licenses (prohibited licenses for an organizations)
* connect workflows to pick-up if such a package or license is found, identify the responsible team with ownership information
NOTE | This is not yet a Software Bill of Material (legally speaking) because it lacks the non-loaded assets. This is part of an upcoming product increment on the AppSec side.
